@startuml
class User {
    +name: String
    +email: String
}

note left of User #Pink
    Pink colored note
end note

note right of User #LightBlue : Blue inline note

note top of User : Top note

note bottom of User
    Bottom note with
    multiple lines
end note

note "Floating note with alias" as N1 #Yellow

class Order

N1 .. Order
@enduml
